{"id":"309916463_Bat_algorithm_with_parameter_adaptation_using_Interval_Type-2_fuzzy_logic_for_benchmark_mathematical_functions","abstract":"In this paper we propose a new method for dynamic parameter adaptation in the bat algorithm (BA). BA is a metaheuristic algorithm inspired by the behavior of micro bats, which has been applied to different optimization problems obtaining good results. In this paper we propose dynamic parameter adaptation of the BA using Interval Type-2 fuzzy logic. Simulation results show that the proposed method using Type-2 fuzzy logic is better in comparison with Type-1 fuzzy logic.","authors":["Jonathan Perez","Fevrier Valdez","Oscar Castillo","Olympia Roeva"],"meta":["September 2016","DOI:10.1109/IS.2016.7737409","Conference: 2016 IEEE 8th International Conference on Intelligent Systems (IS)"],"references":["300482395_Dynamic_parameter_adaptation_in_Ant_Colony_Optimization_using_a_fuzzy_system_for_TSP_problems","287008037_An_optimized_k-means_clustering_technique_using_bat_algorithm","258397338_A_Novel_Hybrid_Bat_Algorithm_with_Harmony_Search_for_Global_Numerical_Optimization","239938256_Improved_Bat_Algorithm_IBA_on_Continuous_Optimization_Problems","235323870_BBA_A_Binary_Bat_Algorithm_for_Feature_Selection","221966275_Bat_Algorithm_for_Multi-objective_Optimisation","45913690_A_New_Metaheuristic_Bat-Inspired_Algorithm","294111872_Modification_of_the_Bat_Algorithm_using_fuzzy_logic_for_dynamical_parameter_adaptation","291990696_Firefly_algorithm_for_unconstrained_optimization","286737028_Optimization_of_the_Type-1_and_Type-2_fuzzy_controller_design_for_the_water_tank_using_the_Bee_Colony_Optimization","270575173_Planning_the_sports_training_sessions_with_the_bat_algorithm","269987738_A_new_modification_approach_on_bat_algorithm_for_solving_optimization_problems","267168641_On_Intuitionistic_Fuzzy_Sets_Theory","259167851_Chaotic_bat_algorithm","257748746_Particle_swarm_optimization_with_dynamic_parameter_adaptation_using_interval_type-2_fu